TiddlyMarker is a handy and flexible tool for bookmarking pages to TiddlyWiki
from Firefox. Specify any arbitrary format, and save or send a tiddler with the
press of a single button.

It's recommended that you install a stable version from addons.mozilla.org:
https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tiddlymarker/

To test the addon directly from this repository:
- Enter about:debugging
- Click "Load Temporary Add-on..."
- Select any file within this directory, such as background.js
Alternatively:
- type `make`
- Enter about:addons
- Select gear menu -> "Install Add-on From File..."
- Choose the generated .xpi